-- Novak Djokovic Beats Lu to Reach Wimbledon Semifinals for Second Time
-- James Cone
-- 2010-06-30T14:01:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/serbia-s-djokovic-defeats-taiwan-s-lu-to-again-reach-wimbledon-semifinals.html

          
          
             Serbia’s Novak Djokovic beat
Taiwan’s Yen-Hsun Lu in straight sets today to reach the
semifinals at the Wimbledon tennis tournament for the 
second time.  
 Djokovic, the No. 3 seed, won 6-3, 6-2, 6-2. The 2008
Australian Open champion previously reached the Wimbledon
semifinals in 2007.  
          
          


  


        